Diamond::

She watched him leave. "Yeah, thanks." She shrugged her shoulders and 
walked out of the lab and went walking down the hall.  She really 
didnn't care where she went right now. She was more or less thinking 
about her situation. She knew that she had let her guard down for a 
handsome face and now wondered how much time she had.  She knew that 
what she rerally needed to do was find out just where and what this 
place really was.  A good hunter knew the terriatory around them. She 
transformed into rattle snake and went exploring the ship.
